## Graph Context Injection (Size-Limited)

Before every query, inject a SMALL slice of graph state into the prompt:
- Top 5 recent Findings (description + confidence)
- Top 5 open Questions (question + priority)
- Top 3 active Hypotheses (statement)
- Active Plan metadata (objective + task count, NOT full task list)

Target: < 500 tokens of injected context. The graph holds full state; 
Claude queries it on demand for details.

